The paper deals with summarization of meetings, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves unsupervised learning, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of constraints and features in the relation learner suggests the involvement of machine learning, which is covered under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with summarization, which is a sub-topic of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
